            <title>[LANG-1745] RandomStringUtils.random() with a negative character index should throw IllegalArgumentException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LANG-1745</link>
                <project id="12310481" key="LANG">Commons Lang</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when RandomStringUtils.random encounters negative index it just keep running all the time(like meeting a dead loop?), hope to raise an exception&lt;/p&gt;

